OL,3,CGnawed crisps found at shop in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe worst mouse infestations ever seen'
OL,6,FA convenience store in Southsea has
OL,7,Fbeen shut down over what's been
OL,8,Fdescribed as 'one of the worst mouse
OL,9,Finfestations ever seen.'
OL,11,FCouncil officers visited Premier
OL,12,FExpress Nice 'n' Fresh, on Victoria
OL,13,FRoad North following a complaint from
OL,14,Fa member of the public.
OL,16,FInside they discovered mouse droppings
OL,17,Fon shelves next to sweets and other
OL,18,Ffood items, and several packets of
OL,19,Fgnawed crisps and snacks on sale.
