OL,4,Cthe worst mouse infestations ever seen'
OL,6,FThe shop was closed down immediately
OL,7,Fand on Thursday 12 February a district
OL,8,Fjudge granted a Hygiene Emergency
OL,9,FProhibition Order which prevents the
OL,10,Fbusiness from trading until the
OL,11,Finfestation has been resolved.
OL,13,FCllr Lee Hunt, Cabinet Member for
OL,14,FCommunity Safety, Leisure and Sport,
OL,15,Fsaid: "The environmental health
OL,16,Fofficer who visited described this as
OL,17,Fone of the worst infestations they
OL,18,Fhave ever seen in a retail business.
