OL,3,CGnawed crisps found at shop in 'one of
OL,4,Cthe worst mouse infestations ever seen'
OL,6,F"Mice can spread diseases such as
OL,7,FSalmonella and Campylobacter through
OL,8,Ftheir droppings and urine, so when
OL,9,Fthey come into contact with open food
OL,10,For contaminate the outside of packets
OL,11,Flike in this case, there is an
OL,12,Fimminent risk of illness to people's
OL,13,Fhealth.
OL,15,F"We want to work with businesses to
OL,16,Fresolve any issues before they get to
OL,17,Fthis dangerous state and have to be
OL,18,Fclosed, and thankfully the vast
OL,19,Fmajority of the city's traders operate
OL,20,Fgood hygiene practices."
